ue=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/web-development\">Web</option><option value=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/architecture\">架构</option><option value=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/basic\">基础技术</option><option value=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/books\">书籍</option><option value=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/tutorial\">教程</option><option value=\"http://top.jobbole.com/\">我要投稿</option><option value=\"http://www.importnew.com/16560.html#\">更多频道 »</option><option value=\"http://ios.jobbole.com/\">- iOS</option><option value=\"http://python.jobbole.com/\">- Python</option><option value=\"http://android.jobbole.com/\">- Android</option><option value=\"http://web.jobbole.com/\">- Web前端</option></select></p></nav></header><h1 style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); margin: -5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Myriad Pro&quot;, Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Java编程入门：前言</h1><p class=\"entry-meta-hide-on-mobile\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2015/08/29 | 分类：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.importnew.com/cat/tutorial\" title=\"查看 教程 中的全部文章\" rel=\"category tag\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">教程</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.importnew.com/16560.html#respond\" title=\"《Java编程入门：前言》上的评论\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">0 条评论</a>&nbsp;| 标签：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.importnew.com/tag/java%e7%bc%96%e7%a8%8b%e5%85%a5%e9%97%a8\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">JAVA编程入门</a></p><p><span class=\"jiathis_txt\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&